HEADWORD: Annotation
<hw>An`no*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>annotatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>annotation</ets>.]</ety> <def>A note,
added by way of comment, or explanation; -- usually in the plural;
<as>as, <ex>annotations</ex> on ancient authors, or on a word or a
passage</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Annotationist</ent>⟦br⟧
